## In the meantime, here are general hardening principles:

### ✅ Input Validation
```javascript
// ❌ Weak
if (input) { process(input); }

// ✅ Strong
const schema = yup.string().required().min(3).max(100).matches(/^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+$/);
const validated = await schema.validate(input);
```

### ✅ Sanitization
```javascript
// Prevent XSS
const sanitized = DOMPurify.sanitize(userInput);
```

### ✅ Type Checking
```javascript
// Use strict typing
const email: string = validateEmail(input);
const age: number = validateAge(input);
```

### ✅ Allowlist (not Blocklist)
```javascript
// ✅ Good - explicit whitelist
const allowedRoles = ['admin', 'user', 'guest'];
if (!allowedRoles.includes(role)) throw new Error();

// ❌ Bad - blacklist
if (role !== 'evil') process(role);
```

### ✅ Database Layer
```javascript
// Use parameterized queries
db.query('SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?', [userId]);
```

